prodNameC: “代首林”人體生長激素放射免疫分析試劑
ingredientsDesc:
1. Coated tubes: 100 tubes. The inner surface of each tube is coated with biotinylated IgG to hGH (mouse monoclonal) directed against an hGH epitope
2. I-125 tracer: 1 vial. The vial contains 11 ml IgG to hGH (mouse monoclonal) labeled with I-125, BSA, horse serum, mouse IgG, phosphate buffer, preservatives and in insert red dye. Radioactivity is 333 KBq (9 μCi).
3. hGH calibrators: 7 vials. The vials contain increasing amounts of hGH , human serum, phosphate buffer and preservatives. hGH concentrations are as follows: 0, 1, 3, 6, 16, 40, 100 μIU/ml (0, 0.5, 1.5, 3, 8, 20, 50 ng/ml).
4. Control serum: 1 vial lyophilized reagent. The vial contains hGH, human serum, phosphate buffered and preservatives. 
5. Wash Buffer: 2 bottles. Each bottle contains 50 ml 0.5% Triton X-100 and saline solution.
applicantName: 泰歷藥品儀器股份有限公司
applicantAddr: 台北市大同區承德路二段81號15樓
efficacy: 定量檢測人體血清或血漿檢體中之生長激素(hGH)。
